{"tid":1932023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"18/3/2020 抵制東方任務","createTime":"2020-03-18T13:04:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T23:41:36.000Z","uid":338095,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"5e11d00016805479e64e715fbcf8a3afc5149372","tid":1932023,"uid":338095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T13:04:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jd3qFnn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJd3qFnn.jpg&h=9605dfe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【抵制東方勸誡任務 😢 18 Mar】<br />\n<br />\n💎勸誡 名將作 勿再落廣告💎<br />\n😢1.派慘 🗣2.洗版（好言相勸）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/EuroSofaMondoo/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FEuroSofaMondoo%2F&d=AthmRk%2BBSDjaWf6zT95BzL2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=43ffc6e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/EuroSofaMondoo/</a><br />\n留意係派慘😢+好言相勸，唔好派嬲再吊人！！！<br />\n留意係派慘😢+好言相勸，唔好派嬲再吊人！！！<br />\n留意係派慘😢+好言相勸，唔好派嬲再吊人！！！<br />\n<br />\n留言template:<br />\n最近得知貴公司因在蘋果日報賣廣告被梁振英及其支持者狙擊，被詛咒「以後冇運行」，本人對此深感遺憾。經過十一月區議會選舉後，民意清晰可見，不論政治立場，在商言商，在蘋果日報、viutv等媒體賣廣告實在是明智之舉。現懇請貴公司繼續選擇代表香港人的媒體，並表明不再在東方日報賣廣告，因為以貴公司產品質素之高，不但無幫襯東方之必要，且會對貴司形象帶來負面影響。<br />\n-------------------------------------------------<br />\n永久抵制名單：<br />\n舒適堡<br />\n草姬<br />\n中科健康國際<br />\n樂生命<br />\n位元堂<br />\n華人藥業<br />\n維特健靈"},{"pid":"3093a2ddf36775740df523a9c014914b9535c9e4","tid":1932023,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T13:05:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a4a0f16c259847c532e06416707081120f73da6d","tid":1932023,"uid":295532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T13:09:11.000Z","msg":"做得一個po，之前全部都係嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"078b3bf32f8776c62a6abe4ec2d960cefd6a607c","tid":1932023,"uid":254988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T13:09:49.000Z","msg":"推"